name: Javascriptinteractivity
tagline: Interactivity with Javascript. A collection of HTML, CSS and JS files that interact with each other.
body:
## Welcome to this project JavaScript Interactivity.
Hi everyone, This project is a collection of the all the work and mini projects accomplished as part of the Interactivity with Javascript Certification. Thank you! 

### How to?
The links on the top dock will take you to all the different pages associated with this self project. 
Give them a try! 

### Can I? 
Yes, you are free to redistribute this project, but for educational purposes only. You are welcome become a contributor to this project, you can also contact me and we can work on a large scale project, together. Sounds fun, right? 
If you’re using GitHub Desktop, simply sync your repository and you’ll see the new branch.

# Authors and Contributors
@[geekidharsh](github.com/geekidharsh) 

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Pages? Check out our [documentation](https://help.github.com/pages) or [contact support](https://github.com/contact) and we’ll help you sort it out.
